  "title": "🌟 Head of Nursing/Assistant Director of Nursing – Eldercare Excellence | 5 day | Central | AWS + Bonuses",
  "description": "<p><strong>🌟 Head of Nursing/Assistant Director of Nursing – Eldercare\nExcellence | 5 day | Central | AWS + Bonuses</strong></p><p>Location: Central </p><p>Work Arrangement: 5-day work week</p><p>Are you a seasoned nursing leader ready to shape the\nfuture of eldercare? Join a well-established facility and take the helm in\ndriving clinical excellence, operational efficiency, and staff development. This is your chance to make a lasting impact on the lives of elderly residents while leading a talented nursing team.</p><p><strong>What You’ll Do:</strong></p><ul><li>Lead and inspire a dedicated nursing team to deliver exceptional resident care.</li><li>Oversee nursing operations, performance, and succession planning.</li><li>Drive continuous improvement initiatives to elevate clinical standards.</li><li>Collaborate with senior management to align nursing strategies with organizational goals.</li><li>Mentor and develop staff, fostering a professional and high-performing environment.</li></ul><p><strong>What We’re Looking For:</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s Degree in Nursing (Master’s preferred)</li><li>15+ years of local experience in hospitals or nursing homes</li><li>Proven experience in project management / healthcare coordination</li><li>Exceptional leadership, communication, and organizational skills</li><li>Track record of operational excellence and staff development</li></ul><p><strong>Why Join Us:</strong></p><ul><li>Attractive salary package with Annual Wage Supplement (AWS) and performance bonuses</li><li>Opportunity to lead a respected nursing team and influence eldercare practices</li><li>5-day work week promoting work-life balance</li></ul><p><strong>Ready to Make an Impact? Apply Now!</strong></p><p>Take the next step in your nursing career and lead with purpose. Apply today to join a team committed to excellence in eldercare!</p><p>Send your resume in MS Word format to: <strong>Vanessa.chua@crew.sg</strong></p><p>Please include your <strong>availability, notice period, and expected salary</strong>.</p><p><em>* Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em></p><p>Vanessa Chua Peng Teng (R25158315)</p><p>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd - CREW by HRnet</p><p>E.A. 24C2435</p>",
